    "body": "Executable means the account has enough balance to cover the costs and the nonce is either the next one in line, or there is a sequence of valid transactions with nonces leading up to the current one.\r\n\r\nNon executable means there's either not enough balance, or there's a nonce gap in the transactions, making the current one unexecutable, even if the block is empty.",
